}
```

8. Global CSS (app/globals.css)

```css
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;

:root {
  --foreground-rgb: 0, 0, 0;
  --background-start-rgb: 214, 219, 220;
  --background-end-rgb: 255, 255, 255;
}

@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
  :root {
    --foreground-rgb: 255, 255, 255;
    --background-start-rgb: 0, 0, 0;
    --background-end-rgb: 0, 0, 0;
  }
}

body {
  color: rgb(var(--foreground-rgb));
  background: linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      transparent,
      rgb(var(--background-end-rgb))
    )
    rgb(var(--background-start-rgb));
}

@layer utilities {
  .text-balance {
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
}
```

9. Package.json Dependencies

Make sure your package.json includes these dependencies:

```json
{
  "dependencies": {
    "next": "14.0.0",
    "react": "^18",
    "react-dom": "^18",
    "tailwindcss": "^3.3.0",
    "typescript": "^5"
  }
}
```

10. Tailwind Config (tailwind.config.js)

```javascript
/** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */
module.exports = {
  content: [
    './pages/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx,mdx}',
    './components/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx,mdx}',
    './app/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx,mdx}',
  ],
  theme: {
    extend: {
      backgroundImage: {
        'gradient-radial': 'radial-gradient(var(--tw-gradient-stops))',
        'gradient-conic':
          'conic-gradient(from 180deg at 50% 50%, var(--tw-gradient-stops))',
      },
    },
  },
  plugins: [],
}
```

This complete e-commerce application includes:

¬∑ Responsive design with Tailwind CSS
¬∑ Product listing on the home page
¬∑ Product detail pages with image gallery
¬∑ Shopping cart functionality
¬∑ Navigation with mobile support
¬∑ Professional footer with multiple sections
¬∑ Interactive components (quantity selectors, add to cart buttons)
¬∑ TypeScript for type safety

To run this application:

1. Create a new Next.js project
2. Replace the default files with the code above
3. Install dependencies: npm install
4. Run the development server: npm run dev

The app will be available at http://localhost:3000
